<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Failure</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container text-center mt-5">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
            <h4 class="alert-heading">Payment Failed!</h4>
            <p>Unfortunately, your payment was not successful. Please try again or contact support if the issue persists.</p>
            <hr>
            <p class="mb-0">We apologize for the inconvenience. You can try booking the appointment again.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/patient/book" class="btn btn-primary">Try Again</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
